<h4>
<img src="Themes/celeste/images/useroff.gif" alt="离线"/>
<a href="?PHPSESSID=36b752c53b0f301795115ca6597f7676&amp;action=profile;u=79120" title="检视会员资料:  黒鉄游帝">黒鉄游帝</a>
